<plot>Behind ivy gates, past state-of-the-art security cameras, and down long private driveways, live the top one-percent wealthiest Americans... or so we imagine. ONE PER CENT, an original documentary, speaks with the top one-percent wealthiest, from old money to new money, from the highly secretive to the universally famous, from millionaires to billionaires, in order to investigate the nuances amongst the top 1%. Featured interviews include Russell Simmons (hip-hop mogul), Rebecca Nanasi (a descendent of Benjamin Franklin), Tyler Ellis (daughter of Perry Ellis), and many more.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?412547</url></doc>
